:::The Destrocons/Falcon/Snare/Hun-Grr/Cyclonus/Scourge/Time Warp:::

::They walk in and look around.  This was a nice looking place.  They see 
Drillbit::
Ramjet: I am Ramjet, current leader of the Destrons. This is part of my 
group, the others are coming.  We have come to discuss an alliance with your 
group.
~~~~~
Hun-Grr: Hun-grr thinks so too, but first we see what happen here.
::Cyclonus and Scourge lower their weapons.  They then see Megatron 
victorious::
Cyclonus: Megatron has won!  He must be the true Megatron if he was able to 
defeat Motormaster. Long live Megatron!
Scourge: Long live Megatron!
Hun-grr: We follow Megatron, because he kinda like Galvatron. Hail Megatron!
~~~~~
Time Warp: Thats even better.  Since were equals, what will i be doing to 
help out?

--part1_86.87c3ad8.27ead84f_boundary
